FBIS3-11675 "drlat057_c_94015" FBIS-LAT-94-057 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 MEXICO Colosio Shot, Killed in Attack During Tijuana Campaign Stop New PRI Candidate Named `Over Time' PA2403143894 Mexico City Canal 13 Television Azteca Network in Spanish 1410 GMT 24 Mar 94 PA2403143894 Mexico City Canal 13 Television Azteca Network in Spanish 1410 GMT 24 Mar 94 Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "Good Morning From Mexico" nescast] [Text] The National Executive Council of the PRI released a communique at 0300 local time today reporting on a meeting with President Salinas. This is the text of a paragraph of the communique on whether another presidential candidate could be designated today: In this private meeting, it was said that the indignation and grief of the PRI will not permit decisions that only PRI members should make. To honor Colosio and in memory of his message of unity and harmony among Mexicans, we will meet our commitments and our political responsibility over time.
